Text: thankyou for the ul. great to see stuff like this, good timely comics are hard to get in aus.

I like finding stuff that isn't always really easy to find, so if there's an issue or two you're looking for, let me know and I'll see if I have it or can find it. Right now I'm trying to find War of the Gods #3 so I can get that set-up, and if not then I'll just scan mine for ul.
